contactsdonationagent(8) System Manager's Manual contactsdonationagent(8)

NAME

contactsdonationagent — contactsdonationagent daemon

DESCRIPTION

contactsdonationagent is used by Maps, Messages, and other apps on the system. It keeps track of recently used email addresses, phone numbers, and locations so you can use them again without adding them to your address book.

This command is not intended to be invoked directly.

January 1, 2017 macOS
